---
// Rodapé verde-mata — tagline, contato, mini-nav e linha de SEO local.
---
<footer>
  <div class="shell grid">
    <div class="col-marca">
      <img src="/images/logo-belie.png" alt="Casa Beliê" width="72" height="72" loading="lazy" />
      <p class="serif tagline">Um belo lugar para viver o que realmente importa.</p>
      <span class="nota-hand" aria-hidden="true">até logo ♡</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Onde fica</h3>
      <p>Rua General Glicério, 131<br/>Laranjeiras, Rio de Janeiro/RJ</p>
      <p class="mini">Atendimento por agendamento.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Fale com a gente</h3>
      <p><a href="https://wa.me/5521996694990?text=Ol%C3%A1!%20Quero%20saber%20mais%20sobre%20festas%20na%20Casa%20Beli%C3%AA%20:)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp (21) 99669-4990</a></p>
      <p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/casabelie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@casabelie no Instagram</a></p>
    </div>
    <nav aria-label="Mapa do site">
      <h3>Navegue</h3>
      <a href="/sobre/">A casa</a>
      <a href="/festas/">Festas</a>
      <a href="/espaco/">Espaço</a>
      <a href="/blog/">Novidades</a>
      <a href="/contato/">Contato</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="shell base">
    <p>Casa de festas infantil em Laranjeiras, Zona Sul do Rio de Janeiro — festas afetivas, sem telas, com quintal verde e luz natural.</p>
    <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Casa Beliê</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer{background:var(--mata);color:var(--papel);padding-top:var(--section-y)}
  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.3fr 1fr 1fr .8fr;gap:clamp(28px,4vw,56px);padding-bottom:48px}
  @media(max-width:900px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
  @media(max-width:560px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .col-marca img{filter:brightness(0) invert(1);height:56px;width:auto;margin-bottom:16px}
  .tagline{font-size:1.3rem;max-width:22ch;margin-bottom:12px}
  .nota-hand{color:var(--manteiga);transform:rotate(-3deg)}
  h3{font-size:1.05rem;margin-bottom:12px;color:var(--manteiga)}
  p{color:rgba(253,250,244,.85);font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:8px}
  .mini{font-size:.83rem;color:rgba(253,250,244,.6)}
  a{color:rgba(253,250,244,.9);text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;padding:2px 0}
  a:hover{color:#fff;text-decoration:underline}
  nav a{display:block;margin-bottom:8px}
  .base{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;border-top:1px solid rgba(253,250,244,.15);padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:24px}
  .base p{font-size:.8rem;color:rgba(253,250,244,.55);margin:0}
</style>
